        </ol></p>
    </section>
    <section class="- topic/section " xtrf="C:\Users\sharmabi\git\documentation\helion\cinder\vsa\vsa.dita" xtrc="section:4;97:14">
      <title class="- topic/title " xtrf="C:\Users\sharmabi\git\documentation\helion\cinder\vsa\vsa.dita" xtrc="title:5;98:14">Configure VSA as a Cinder Backend</title>
      <p class="- topic/p " xtrf="C:\Users\sharmabi\git\documentation\helion\cinder\vsa\vsa.dita" xtrc="p:14;99:10">You must modify <codeph class="+ topic/ph pr-d/codeph " xtrf="C:\Users\sharmabi\git\documentation\helion\cinder\vsa\vsa.dita" xtrc="codeph:5;99:34">cinder.conf.j2</codeph> to update VSA cluster.</p>
      <p class="- topic/p " xtrf="C:\Users\sharmabi\git\documentation\helion\cinder\vsa\vsa.dita" xtrc="p:15;100:10">Perform the following steps to update the VSA cluster:<ol id="ol_dj2_qcz_ht" class="- topic/ol " xtrf="C:\Users\sharmabi\git\documentation\helion\cinder\vsa\vsa.dita" xtrc="ol:4;100:87">
          <li class="- topic/li " xtrf="C:\Users\sharmabi\git\documentation\helion\cinder\vsa\vsa.dita" xtrc="li:29;101:15">Login to deployer node.</li>
          <li class="- topic/li " xtrf="C:\Users\sharmabi\git\documentation\helion\cinder\vsa\vsa.dita" xtrc="li:30;102:15">Change the directory as shown below:<codeblock xml:space="preserve" class="+ topic/pre pr-d/codeblock " xtrf="C:\Users\sharmabi\git\documentation\helion\cinder\vsa\vsa.dita" xtrc="codeblock:5;102:62">cd ~/helion</codeblock></li>
          <li class="- topic/li " xtrf="C:\Users\sharmabi\git\documentation\helion\cinder\vsa\vsa.dita" xtrc="li:31;103:15">Edit  <codeph class="+ topic/ph pr-d/codeph " xtrf="C:\Users\sharmabi\git\documentation\helion\cinder\vsa\vsa.dita" xtrc="codeph:6;103:29">my_cloud/config/cinder/cinder.conf.j2</codeph> to add VSA data as
            follows:<codeblock xml:space="preserve" class="+ topic/pre pr-d/codeblock " xtrf="C:\Users\sharmabi\git\documentation\helion\cinder\vsa\vsa.dita" xtrc="codeblock:6;104:32"># Configure the enabled backends
enabled_backends=vsa-1</codeblock></li>
          <li class="- topic/li " xtrf="C:\Users\sharmabi\git\documentation\helion\cinder\vsa\vsa.dita" xtrc="li:32;106:15">Copy VSA section, uncomment it, and modify the values in the
              <codeph class="+ topic/ph pr-d/codeph " xtrf="C:\Users\sharmabi\git\documentation\helion\cinder\vsa\vsa.dita" xtrc="codeph:7;107:23">cinder.conf.j2</codeph> file as shown in the following
              example:<codeblock id="vssa-config" xml:space="preserve" class="+ topic/pre pr-d/codeblock " xtrf="C:\Users\sharmabi\git\documentation\helion\cinder\vsa\vsa.dita" xtrc="codeblock:7;108:51">[vsa-1]
hplefthand_password: &lt;password given during cluster creation&gt;
hplefthand_clustername: &lt;VSA cluster name&gt;
hplefthand_api_url: https://&lt;store virtual virtual ip&gt;:8081/lhos
hplefthand_username: &lt;username given during cluster creation&gt;
hplefthand_iscsi_chap_enabled: true
